        <unitName xml:lang="en">kg</unitName>
        <comment xml:lang="en">Total amount of active substance/s of fertilisers needed for the production of 'rice' is calculated to be circa 1.72E-02 kg. Fertiliser/s used in this dataset is/are: 'nitrogen fertiliser, as N', 'phosphate fertiliser, as P2O5', 'urea, as N'. The total amount of active substance/s is doubled in order to account for the packaging of the dilluted product of fertiliser/s that is/are applied. Therefore, 3.44E-02 kg of packaging for fertilisers is justified with this exchange.</comment>
